products.title: Unilux PVC Blackout Cream Velux Keylite Fakro Dakstra
products.description: Their unilux pvc blackout roof blinds come in their most popular colour options - a great way for you to upgrade your skylight window at a value cost. This option comes with sleek, modern aluminium framework. This flame retardant fabric has an fibreglass core and provides up to 20% heat loss reduction.
